// algorithm file for final project

create tamagotchi with egg form
egg form
	evolve to next form
baby form
	evolve to next form
	or run away
teenage form
	evolve to next form
	or run away
adult form
	evolve to next form
	or run away
senior form
	run away

run until egg hatches
after egg hatches
	Automatic:
		chance to decrease hunger
		chance to sleep
		chance to call for attention
		chance to get sick
		run away if sad for too long
		run away if hungry for too long
		evolve if weight and happiness is good
	User:
		chance to heal sickness
		feed meal or snack
		play with tamagotchi

display stats and options after every user input
